RelatedSentence: Two people are dead after a woman crashed her car into a tree in southwest Houston .
According to the Houston Police Department , Sairi Orellana was driving a Chevrolet Blazer erratically when she swerved off the road and into a ditch .
The vehicle then ran into a tree before flipping over .
Police say Orellana was not wearing a seat belt and was thrown from the car as it rolled over .
